    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1013">
<l>ūṉaik kuṟitta tuyirellā nāṇeṉṉu</l>
<l>naṉmai kuṟittatu cālpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the body is the abode of the spirit, so the excellence of modesty is the abode of perfection.</l>
